# Standalone sibling apps (reranker, model-manager) are deployed separately and
# are not part of the Ask image. Excluding them keeps the Ask build context
# small (the model-manager alone carries ~840MB of node_modules) and prevents
# the build from ever picking up their sources.
selfhosted/

# Scratch/state that must never enter the image or the build context.
.superpowers/
.claude/
.git/
